high_descs: Take the apple from the fridge.
Turn left and go to the counter, then turn left and go forward, then turn right and face the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Turn around and go forward to the wall, then turn right to face the table.
Put the apple on the table, to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple on the table.

high_descs: Walk straight and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and take the apple then close the fridge
Turn left walk straight then head to the sink on your right
Put the apple in the sink and rinse it
Turn right walk straight then face the table on your right
Put the apple on the table left side of the bread
anns.task_desc: Put the clean apple on the table

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Turn around a walk around the left side of the table.
Place the apple on the table to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple on a table.
